# RELEASE

## Version: 1.0.0
- Modernized EPC result UI with per-tag card rows and count badges.
- Added count threshold badge coloring for high-volume tag visibility.
- Hidden top Unique/Total summary bar in favor of per-row count display.
- Added `suspend_resume_device.sh` utility for ADB suspend/resume workflows.
- Hardened `build_deploy_launch.sh` for wrapper recovery and robust device detection.
- Updated documentation for DataWedge requirements, tested platforms, and compatibility matrix.
- Date: May 26, 2026

## Version: 0.0.1
- Modularized DataWedge intent handling (DataWedgeHelper)
- Improved user feedback (Toasts, dialogs)
- Progress dialog for scanning operations
- Documentation and onboarding improvements
- Date: March 29, 2026

## Version: 0.0.2
- Consolidated DataWedge Notification API for real-time hardware status monitoring.
- Implemented dual-status UI for Barcode Scanner and RFID Sled.
- Added explicit SET_CONFIG result handling to detect missing hardware.
- Modernized status bar UI with color-coded indicators.
- Fixed duplicate class and package name conflicts.
- Date: April 2, 2026
